        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and transfer it to a large bowl</p><p>Drizzle over some <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
