      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a fan of raw garlic? Just add a little!), <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon</strong>, season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> remaining lemon </strong>into wedges and set aside for later</p>",
